    metaDescription: "Learn why FDA-approved devices matter for your safety and results at a med spa. Rani Beauty Clinic in Renton, WA uses only approved technology.",
    excerpt: "FDA-approved devices undergo rigorous testing for safety and effectiveness. Here is why that matters when you are choosing a med spa for your treatments.",
